      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MODEL FERNANDA (4) jumped from box 8 last time and ran away with an impressive win scoring by 4.5 lengths at this track in a handy 18.89. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Can continue on her winning ways. RUN BINDI RUN (8) three runs back clocked a slick 18.90 win over 330m at this track then has found the minor money in two runs since. Has the ability and looks a key chance. ASTON JOE (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (18.87) at Dubbo behind Bronte Beach in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Expected to be in the finish again. WHAT EVER (5) is always a threat when she races at this journey.",
